voted out they'll move over

00:52:24.288 --> 00:52:27.010
to this think tank and they
wait for another cycle.

00:52:27.010 --> 00:52:28.250
And they all come back in.

00:52:28.250 --> 00:52:29.530
So you don't get the 2.6.

00:52:29.530 --> 00:52:31.360
